    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Mar 27, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-27/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Mar 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-03-27/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;functionality Enhanced Log Management in cloudhub is not visible&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Runtime verion 3.7.3. For mobile services on cloud we are able to see only &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://forums.mulesoft.com/questions/61682/functionality-enhanced-log-management-in-cloudhub.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://forums.mulesoft.com/questions/61682/functionality-enhanced-log-management-in-cloudhub.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Putting Private Back in Private Cloud With Industry-First End-to-End&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Digital Journal The number of breaches within the US have quadrupled in the last ten years, and last year accounted for seven of the ten biggest data breaches ever.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3283481&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3283481&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Get ready for 2018&amp;rsquo;s changes to data protection laws&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have you adequate systems in place to manage data breaches that may arise and to comply with the notification requirements? The GDPR requires &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www2.cipd.co.uk/pm/peoplemanagement/b/weblog/archive/2017/03/27/get-ready-for-2018-s-changes-to-data-protection-laws.aspx&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www2.cipd.co.uk/pm/peoplemanagement/b/weblog/archive/2017/03/27/get-ready-for-2018-s-changes-to-data-protection-laws.aspx&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Multi-State Data Breach Linked To Labor Boards&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the interesting trends in identity theft and data breaches is in the industries that are targeted. In 2016, it was the year of the medical facility, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://news.filehippo.com/2017/03/multi-state-data-breach-linked-to-labor-boards/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://news.filehippo.com/2017/03/multi-state-data-breach-linked-to-labor-boards/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Best practice lays the foundation for defence&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sophos&amp;rsquo;s Security Heartbeat ensures your endpoint protection and firewall are talking to each other. It&amp;rsquo;s a simple yet effective idea that means you &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://blogs.sophos.com/2017/03/27/best-practice-lays-the-foundation-for-defence/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://blogs.sophos.com/2017/03/27/best-practice-lays-the-foundation-for-defence/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;problme de mise  jour Symantec endpoint protection avce Windows 10&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fonctionne pas au niveau de Windows 10. j&amp;rsquo;ai excut Sym diag , il m&amp;rsquo;a affich &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/probleme-de-mise-jour-symantec-endpoint-protection-avce-windows-10&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.symantec.com/connect/forums/probleme-de-mise-jour-symantec-endpoint-protection-avce-windows-10&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How MasterCard is preparing Middle East businesses for cyber attacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; simulate a cyberattack to provide participants with a first-hand experience in dealing with data breaches which are growing ever more sophisticated &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businessreviewmiddleeast.com/technology/915/How-MasterCard-is-preparing-Middle-East-businesses-for-cyber-attacks&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.businessreviewmiddleeast.com/technology/915/How-MasterCard-is-preparing-Middle-East-businesses-for-cyber-attacks&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Toward Strategic and Proactive Threat Intelligence Programs&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Threat hunting. Armed with knowledge about which threat-actors are attacking and the weapons they tend to use, security analysts can engage in &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3185209/security/toward-strategic-and-proactive-threat-intelligence-programs.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.networkworld.com/article/3185209/security/toward-strategic-and-proactive-threat-intelligence-programs.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;European CISOs facing challenge to protect employee data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nearly a quarter (22%) either do not believe data breaches incur a cost to their employers, or are unsure; with France and the UK representing the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.information-age.com/cisos-challenge-protect-employee-123465298/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.information-age.com/cisos-challenge-protect-employee-123465298/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Laptops containing 3.7 million Hong Kong voters&amp;rsquo; data stolen after chief&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;South China Morning Post In what could be one of Hong Kong&amp;rsquo;s most significant data breaches ever, the personal information of the city&amp;rsquo;s 3.7 million voters was possibly &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2082566/laptops-containing-37-million-hong-kong-voters-data-stolen&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2082566/laptops-containing-37-million-hong-kong-voters-data-stolen&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Cyber and privacy risks for professional firms&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In December 2016, the SRA revealed that Friday afternoon frauds represented 75% of all data breaches reported by law firms. Although breaches on &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=4530bb43-31df-4da8-92ed-7d010f409db2&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.lexology.com/library/detail.aspx?g=4530bb43-31df-4da8-92ed-7d010f409db2&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Get prepared for a new world of data protection&lt;/h3&gt;
